title: THE 2ND GREAT WAR - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Skyrim Campaign #1
description:

And the Kingdoms of Skyrim is united once again.  It is time to destroy the Aldemri Dominion.  Welcome to the 2nd Great War!  Enjoy the Episode :D
